text:
Covered, at survey depth:

- EPSO's role and the current (post-2023) selection procedure for permanent
  officials, as published on eu-careers.europa.eu, verified 2026-07-19.
- The EPSO Competency Framework (2022 edition) — the 8 general competencies.
- How the institutions assess competencies: written tests at selection;
  interviews at recruitment; the legacy SCBI format.
- Contract-agent (CAST) selection vs official selection, at survey level.
- Brief orientation on competency interviews in EU private-sector and
  multinational employers.

Not covered (deliberately): anchor-level analysis of each competency;
assessment-centre exercise design; EU agencies' individual procedures;
temporary-agent selection; UK frameworks (see `uk-frameworks-foundation`);
detailed interview technique (see `techniques-foundation`).
